data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Price Improvement!!! If you have been looking for to your own place in a Golf Cart Friendly, 55+ Community of Lake Frances Estates....YA FOUND THE ONE!!! This two bedroom, two bathroom home has luxury vinyl flooring throughout. A separate over-sized laundry room off of the carport/screen porch area. The back yard is fully fenced with chain link fencing. The two storage sheds offer plenty of space to store your goodies. The community itself has a very nice clubhouse that boasts a kitchen, billiards room, card tables, and an indoor pool. Right outside of the clubhouse you will find a grand community pool, large dock, shuffleboard courts, and access to Lake Frances. Get your social calendar ready because there are events that occur regularly at the clubhouse that you won't want to miss! It's just a short golf cart ride to the heart of Tavares, where you can enjoy all of the downtown entertainment, restaurants, happenings and seaplanes. The City of Tavares hosts several events throughout the year and allows for open containers within certain specifications in the Downtown Waterfront Entertainment District area. This location also allows for quick access grocery stores and shopping, along with a close proximity to the Florida Waterman Hospital.
